br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7X6fsR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7X6fsR.jpg&h=12d21402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HNGrfsS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHNGrfsS.jpg&h=4cfe0a4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d3e08ccb2cf32a0eb60dd410350908645f39d44","tid":1788784,"uid":182615,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"造假造票團粉絲wiz*one  跟埋IZONE一齊造票<br />\n真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}